  <brief_title>Chemotherapy and Radiation Therapy in Treating Patients With Stomach Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial of Preoperative Chemotherapy and Chemoradiotherapy for Potentially Resectable Adenocarcinoma of the Stomach</official_title>
